data.description: Welcome to 243 Shady Oak Grove, where comfort meets convenience in this charming top-floor unit. This 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom gem includes a convenient designated parking spot and one-car detached garage, ensuring hassle-free parking. As you step inside this inviting condo, you'll be greeted by an impressive open layout that seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas, creating an ideal space for both entertaining guests and unwinding after a hectic day. The living space boasts a bright and welcoming ambiance, accentuated by new LED kitchen lighting and modern fixtures in the kitchen and bathrooms. New flooring has also recently been installed in the bathrooms and second bedroom. Notable updates include a newly installed hot water heater and garbage disposal, both added in 2022. Furthermore, the A/C, furnace, and plumbing have all been serviced as of April 2024. Step outside onto your private balcony and immerse yourself in the serene surroundings. Residents of Sand Creek Commons also enjoy exclusive access to a community playground and picnic area, providing ample opportunities for outdoor relaxation and enjoyment. Nestled in the heart of Colorado Springs, this residence offers more than just a home; it provides a lifestyle upgrade. Its central location near shopping centers, entertainment options, and military bases ensures easy access to everything you need for a fulfilling lifestyle. Don't miss the opportunity to make this delightful residence your own. Schedule a showing today and experience the ease of living in the heart of town!
